=Description=

"The Institute for Evolutionary Leadership (IEL) is an emerging community of practice that develops and supports leaders who redesign cultures and institutions for a more just, sustainable, and flourishing world. IEL was established in 2014 in Oakland, CA. It currently operates as a Limited Liability Company while building community, model, and structure that would enable it to transform into a cooperative."
